DIRTY TRICKS
Type: Combat Action
See also: <help combat actions>

You have abandoned any pretense of honor in combat, and strive to win
against your opponent using the knife and any ruthless, dirty trick
you can bring to bear.

Skilled assassins inevitably emerge from Gurov.
1   : bumrush (target)
1   : shiv (target)
25  : hock (on target)
50  : dust
75  : conspire (with ally)
100 : fade
200 : gouge (target)

